Confirmed to be useful for checking header accuracy:

(\p{Thai}) # matches any thai, confirmed in regex101.com
(\p{Han}) # matches any kanji/hanzi
(\p{Hebrew})|(\p{Armenian})
(\p{Bengali})
(\p{Gujarati})
(\p{Greek})
(\p{Hiragana})
(\p{Hangul})
(\p{Katakana})|
(\p{Kannada})
(\p{Malayalam})|
(\p{Tamil})
(\p{Telugu})

